2164.subject: MLML
2164.descrlong:
MLML 105:Marine Sci Divng- Skin and SCUBA diving course. Pool training culminates in ten ocean dives. Topics covered include diving physics, physiology, diving environments, night diving, and research diving. Successful completion gives NAUI and MLML certification. Not for major credit. (Offered every semester.)

(Prereq: Exclude Freshman and Sophomore and Junior)
